href="jonmsterling.xml"
addr="jonmsterling"
title="Jon Sterling">Jonathan Sterling</fr:link> has been selected as the winner of the 2022 Edmund M. Clarke Dissertation Award in CSD for his thesis:</fr:p><fr:p><fr:link
type="local"
href="sterling-2021-thesis.xml"
addr="sterling-2021-thesis"
title="First steps in synthetic Tait computability: the objective metatheory of cubical type theory">First Steps in Synthetic Tait Computability</fr:link>, October 2021</fr:p><fr:p><fr:link
