href="jonmsterling.xml"
addr="jonmsterling"
title="Jon Sterling">Jonathan</fr:link>’s PhD research was advised by <fr:link
type="local"
href="robertharper.xml"
addr="robertharper"
title="Robert Harper">Robert Harper</fr:link>.</fr:p><fr:p>This award, endowed by a generous contribution from Professor Ed Clarke and his wife Martha, is given annually to an outstanding dissertation in the Computer Science Department.</fr:p><fr:p>Congratulations <fr:link
type="local"
href="jonmsterling.xml"
addr="jonmsterling"
title="Jon Sterling">Jonathan</fr:link>!</fr:p></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree><fr:tree
