text="First steps in synthetic Tait computability: the objective metatheory of cubical type theory">First steps in synthetic Tait computability: the objective metatheory of cubical type theory</fr:title><fr:taxon>Reference</fr:taxon><fr:date><fr:year>2021</fr:year><fr:month>9</fr:month><fr:day>13</fr:day></fr:date><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link
